# SEO & AEO

## Structured Data (JSON-LD)

Schemas live in `src/pages/index.astro` frontmatter and inject via the `<BaseHead>` slot:
- `Organization` — business name, Barrie ON address, contact, logo
- `FAQPage` — all FAQ items; add new Q&A to the `faqItems` array

## Meta Tags

Pass via `<BaseLayout>` props — `BaseHead` handles title, description, canonical, OG, Twitter Card:

```astro
<BaseLayout
  title="Page Title | Techshift AI Consulting"
  description="150-160 char description"
>
```

## AEO Files — Update on Every Content Change

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `src/pages/llms.txt.ts` | Markdown index for AI crawlers |
| `src/pages/llms-full.txt.ts` | Full plaintext content (~5.6 KB) |

Both must reflect any new or changed content.

## Heading Hierarchy

- Single `<h1>` per page — always in the hero
- Sections use `<h2>` with `id` matching `aria-labelledby` on the `<section>`
- Never skip levels
